div.h1: Page Fault Handling: CR2 and Error Code

div.p:
Error Code Bits:
I R U W P
Present (0=not present) Write (1=write access) User (1=user mode) Reserved bit set Instruction fetch (NX)
SS (if CPL change) ESP (if CPL change) EFLAGS CS EIP Error Code pushed by CPU
===== PAGE FAULT ===== Faulting address: 0xDEADBEEF Error code: 0x07
Cause: Page not present Access type: Write Mode: User
